gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 121, Grizzlies 101
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Grizzlies, 121-101. Jonathan Kuminga led the Warriors with 29 points, six rebounds, and four assists as Stephen Curry (20 points, six rebounds, six assists) and Brandin Podziemski (12 points, career-high 14 assists, seven rebounds) totaled 32 points. Jaren Jackson Jr. led the Grizzlies with 27 points and five rebounds.
